00:00:15,600 --> 00:00:16,760
Promise me,

2
00:00:17,480 --> 00:00:18,960
no matter what happens,

3
00:00:19,400 --> 00:00:20,480
protect yourself first.

4
00:00:23,960 --> 00:00:24,800
Okay.

5
00:00:25,640 --> 00:00:26,600
I promise you.

6
00:00:30,720 --> 00:00:31,560
He's coming.

7
00:00:39,480 --> 00:00:40,360
You're here.

8
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:42,840
Let's go.

9
00:00:51,700 --> 00:00:56,140
=Above The Clouds=

10
00:00:56,260 --> 00:00:58,380
=Episode 20=

11
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:12,000
You've finally arrived.

12
00:01:17,320 --> 00:01:18,400
So you're Xi Yue.

13
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,880
Did you remember me,

14
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:24,680
or did you investigate and find out?

15
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:30,120
What grudge lies between us

16
00:01:30,960 --> 00:01:33,200
that you torment me in every lifetime?

17
00:01:34,480 --> 00:01:35,320
Grudge?

18
00:01:39,720 --> 00:01:42,560
There's no grudge between us.

19
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:44,720
If there's no grudge,

20
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:47,040
then is it your pastime

21
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:49,360
to toy with others' fates for fun?

22
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:52,680
Exactly. Your fate was too good

23
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:54,080
and I couldn't stand it,

24
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:55,840
so I altered it.

25
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:02,240
Who would've thought you were so stubborn?

26
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,960
You just had to defy fate,

27
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:06,360
and actually succeeded.

28
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,320
But this time,

29
00:02:10,480 --> 00:02:12,990
I wonder if you'll be as lucky.

30
00:02:14,480 --> 00:02:15,320
What do you mean?

31
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:18,740
What do you think?

32
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:31,280
Didn't you say that if I gave up
the Luminous Heart,

33
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:32,800
you'd help me change fate?

34
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:36,600
But I was lying.

35
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:40,160
You...

36
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:47,280
What, planning to hit me?

37
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,280
Do you even deserve to?

38
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:55,040
You're nothing more than an ant.

39
00:02:56,160 --> 00:02:57,920
With one lift of my foot,

40
00:02:58,680 --> 00:03:00,920
I could crush you like dust.

41
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,720
Trying to fight me?

42
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:05,600
How foolish.

43
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:07,760
Yu Han,

44
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:12,160
activate the array.

45
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:13,120
Fuse the divine artifacts.

46
00:03:13,480 --> 00:03:14,320
Yes.

47
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:02,840
She's absorbing the power of the artifacts!

48
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:05,400
Yu Han, stop her!

49
00:04:22,170 --> 00:04:27,970
♪Dreams linger in memories untold♪

50
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:30,920
So that's why

51
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,910
you agreed to change fate.

52
