♪Your face in moonlight♪

53
00:04:37,650 --> 00:04:40,570
♪So close, yet cold♪

54
00:04:40,930 --> 00:04:46,170
♪Trapped in amber, love turned to stone♪

55
00:04:48,210 --> 00:04:51,590
♪A ghost of you pierces my soul♪

56
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:52,440
Ling Cang,

57
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:54,000
leave me be.

58
00:04:54,690 --> 00:04:58,970
♪Tears cling, refusing to fall♪

59
00:05:00,490 --> 00:05:03,610
♪Through cycles of time♪

60
00:05:03,970 --> 00:05:06,650
♪I'd still choose you above all♪

61
00:05:07,210 --> 00:05:10,210
♪So I'll shatter♪

62
00:05:10,690 --> 00:05:12,760
♪The mirrors of destiny's hand♪

63
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:17,960
Stop!

64
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:22,520
Your body can't withstand the power
of all four artifacts!

65
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:27,960
Who are you?

66
00:05:28,280 --> 00:05:30,240
I am the spirit of the divine artifacts.

67
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,800
When the four

68
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:33,320
divine artifacts merge,

69
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:36,400
I awaken from slumber.

70
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:40,400
Heed my warning, stop now.

71
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:45,680
If you truly wish to change everything,

72
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:48,320
you must return to ten thousand years ago.

73
00:05:48,520 --> 00:05:50,040
Ten thousand years ago?

74
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:51,520
Indeed.

75
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:56,480
All karma stems from a catastrophe back then.

76
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:58,280
If you can alter it,

77
00:05:58,600 --> 00:06:00,520
you can change everything,

78
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:03,240
including your fate with Ye Sha.

79
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:08,720
How do I go back?

80
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:12,400
Let me help you.

81
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,080
Xi Yue!

82
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:27,800
Xi Yue!

83
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:28,880
Xi Yue!

84
00:06:59,780 --> 00:07:03,540
(Jing Yun, Celestial Sovereign)

85
00:07:03,540 --> 00:07:07,180
(Divine Retribution Altar, Divine Realm)

86
00:07:07,380 --> 00:07:09,820
(Xi Yue, Divine Attendant)

87
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:19,640
This is...

88
00:07:20,640 --> 00:07:22,160
The Divine Realm from ten thousand years ago.

89
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:30,440
Xi Yue,

90
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,400
as one of the Divine Realm,

91
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:34,120
you secretly practiced demonic arts

92
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:36,120
and broke divine laws.

93
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:38,560
Do you admit your guilt?

94
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:42,880
I trained in demonic arts

95
00:07:43,840 --> 00:07:45,040
only to further my cultivation.

96
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,240
What crime is that?

97
00:07:52,520 --> 00:07:53,880
Ages ago,

98
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:55,880
