99
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:57,480
Why are we

100
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:59,120
enemies now?

101
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:02,560
Still arguing?

102
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,120
Anning,

103
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:10,480
why are you...

104
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:13,600
Master, eons ago,

105
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:15,080
gods and demons were never divided.

106
00:08:15,590 --> 00:08:16,990
Only self-interest

107
00:08:17,080 --> 00:08:19,390
caused today's hatred.

108
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:23,040
So how is practicing divine arts
any different from demonic ones?

109
00:08:23,880 --> 00:08:25,960
You shouldn't punish Xi Yue.

110
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:30,760
Seems I've spoiled you too much.

111
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:33,760
You dare defy your master

112
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,840
and disobey orders?

113
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:43,840
Then I'll teach you a proper lesson today.

114
00:08:59,880 --> 00:09:00,720
Ye Sha, the Demon Sovereign?

115
00:09:01,860 --> 00:09:04,860
